*&quot;The World of Bertoia&quot; (2003), Nancy N. Schiffer and Val O. Bertoia, Schiffer Publishing, 
* &quot;The Life and Work of Harry Bertoia &quot;(2015), Celia Bertoia, Schiffer Publishing, 

